ūüĎ¶ Nephew: That's a lot! Where do I start?

ūüĎ®‚Äćūü¶≥ Uncle: With step 1. Let's go slow. The foundation must be solid.

PHASE 1, STEP 1-2: Document Upload & File Hashing

Why Does File Hashing Matter?

ūüĎ¶ Nephew: Why hash a file? Why not just upload it?

ūüĎ®‚Äćūü¶≥ Uncle: Because humans are lazy. The HR person uploads the same PDF three times. Your system processes it three times. Three embeddings created. Three times the cost.

ūüĎ¶ Nephew: So hash prevents duplicates?

ūüĎ®‚Äćūü¶≥ Uncle: Yes. But here's the trick: don't hash the filename.

ūüĎ¶ Nephew: Why not?

ūüĎ®‚Äćūü¶≥ Uncle: Because someone could change the content and keep the same name. Look:

File: HR_Policy.pdf (Version 1)
Content: "30 days notice required"
Filename Hash: HR_Policy.pdf
File: HR_Policy.pdf (Version 2)
Content: "7 days notice required"
Filename Hash: HR_Policy.pdf (SAME!)
System thinks: Same file!
Reality: Different policies!

