Exit fullscreen mode

That's a disaster.

ūüĎ¶ Nephew: So we hash the content?

ūüĎ®‚Äćūü¶≥ Uncle: Yes. The actual binary data.

HR_Policy.pdf (Version 1)
‚Üď
[PDF binary bytes: 0xAA 0xBB 0xCC ...]
